public class CatalogAvailabilityNode
extends CatalogHierarchyNode

This object represents the availability node in an availability tree. It extends the common tree node CatalogHierarchyNode, which in turn is a CatalogItem.

Method Detail

isAvailable

public com.conceptwave.scripting.Boolean isAvailable(String code)
This method is only supported if the CwcItem is an instance of CwcAvailabilityNodeItem(Availabilty Node). It checks whether an item specified by the code is available for the current availability node.

Parameters:
code - code for the item that is checking for availability
Returns:
true if item is available for the Availability Node, and false if the item is not available
